### Performance Considerations
- Network latency between services
- Proper load balancing and caching strategies

### Security Considerations
- Service-to-service authentication and authorization
- Secure communication channels (e.g., HTTPS, mTLS)
- Isolation of services to prevent breaches from propagating

### Scalability Considerations
- Horizontal scaling of individual services based on demand
- Stateless design for easy scaling
- Proper monitoring and auto-scaling mechanisms

